,{"pid":"42975753944d0a7ae9e6bb454f3162b4a7904dce","tid":249004,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"唐寧完勝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79855771c030919406b3e74406b0499858bab0b","tid":249004,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:13:55.000Z","msg":"整容雞垃圾<br />\n<br />\n唐寧生完後種人妻feel好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1da1bf01f4269b66ae1aca0c96f9556699133d9b","tid":249004,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>李一桐隻眼同果個簡乜乜隻眼一樣樣</blockquote><br />\n原來唔係得我一個咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎緊幾年可能興咁樣整<br />\n而家AB個模支那通街都係"},{"pid":"93be36b5f2bb1f05e16087f8b40e0ded67e32ad2","tid":249004,"uid":35370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:17:41.000Z","msg":"整容樣點同師妃媗比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"414d9a9a582ab441713a51630f799c8112c92e80","tid":249004,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打咁比較公平咩 ? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n師妃暄個角色唔計演員本身個設定就應該有仙氣過黃蓉 <br />\n一個係靜齋既傳人 一個係有個霸氣老豆既刁蠻佻皮女<br />\n點比啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我有諗過用劉亦菲個小龍女比，因為個feel似啲同埋公認屈機，不過呢排射雕hit，所以就用李一桐先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf521d225af9e8b01041ddb8ef5cc47a507a3b81","tid":249004,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>李一桐隻眼同果個簡乜乜隻眼一樣樣</blockquote><br />\n原來唔係得我一個咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黎緊幾年可能興咁樣整<br />\n而家AB個模支那通街都係</blockquote><br />\n你貼幾張圖黎睇下點樣支那通街都係似AB個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647c06c428b5412cc15aceb00daf773f0a0609bc","tid":249004,"uid":43427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T04:37:18.000Z","msg":"公平咩<br />\n攞唐寧同隻唔知咩嘅野比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b51d65d981f6d928551f293aa540d56a472ca1a","tid":249004,"uid":4180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T12:21:22.000Z","msg":"唐寧完勝啦"},{"pid":"6034c81ffe8a6c3af615a9b49d7116c084f24543","tid":249004,"uid":7466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:04:16.000Z","msg":"又到吹捧舊人時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d84172be37c3d14913be73afc2dc43da7223d4e","tid":249004,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:19:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又到吹捧舊人時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢青"},{"pid":"fe8a51d3338cb65ac86164f67305bc20c8c2ec35","tid":249004,"uid":57132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:48:03.000Z","msg":"唐寧真係好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1131d6f31850ca9068ee6c03e4787853480e7f08","tid":249004,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"唐寧無得輸喎"},{"pid":"6948cc0cb7948081175060570c9f4d9f82f3e021","tid":249004,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T13:50:51.000Z","msg":"唐寧無得輸喎"},{"p